Ex-100m national champions Mokamba and Otieno highlight 31-man Kenyan squadCoach Mwaniki to help Kenyan athletes refine key skills ahead of the May 1-2 championship planned for Silesia, Poland Head coach Steven Mwaniki has said that the next two weeks will be crucial for Team Kenya athletes as they prepare for the World Relay Championships due May 1 to 2 in Silesia, Poland. 



